  "prompt": "Which are the least expensive and still good 3D/4D cinema theaters in Delhi NCR?",
  "response": "Finding an affordable yet high-quality 3D/4D cinema experience in the Delhi NCR region can vary based on the latest deals, days of the week, and theater-specific promotions. As of the latest information, some of the theaters that are known for offering good cinema experiences at reasonable prices include:\n\n1. **PVR Cinemas**: Widely regarded for its quality, PVR offers various theaters across Delhi NCR, often with deals through their app or loyalty programs. They periodically have discounts, especially during weekdays or off-peak hours.\n\n2. **INOX**: Another popular chain, INOX provides good 3D/4D experiences. Look out for special offers and card promotions which can make visits more economical.\n\n3. **Carnival Cinemas**: Known for competitive pricing and decent quality, Carnival Cinemas often runs discounts and offers on ticket bookings.\n\n4. **Cinepolis**: With several locations, Cinepolis offers a high-quality experience. They also run various promotions and discounts, particularly for online bookings.\n\n5. **M2K Cinemas**: Though not as widespread, M2K offers an affordable cinematic experience with occasional offers.\n\n6. **Wave Cinemas**: Known for good value for money, Wave Cinemas frequently have promotional offers that can reduce costs significantly.\n\nFor the most accurate and current pricing, it is advisable to check their official websites, apps, or third-party booking platforms such as BookMyShow, where you can often find discount codes or bank offers. Additionally, keep an eye on weekdays and matinee shows, as they typically offer the best prices.",
